## Problem Statement

```figure caption="A grey-atmosphere column with incoming solar radiation S/4, reflected fraction α(T)S/4, and outgoing longwave radiation εσT⁴. The albedo α(T) has a sigmoidal transition from ice-covered (α_cold≈0.6) to ice-free (α_warm≈0.3) across T_c≈263 K. The energy balance yields three equilibria for present-day solar constant."
